 *      - Added new Correcting creature weapons animations routine that patches vanilla creature files with new cloned weapons compatible with their animations (#414).                *
 *      - ToBEx compatibility: checks for ToBEx external walking sound files (#192) and resolves soundsets creature animation conflicts (#401).                                        *
 *      - Externalized lists of creatures to be patched into arrays for easier maintenance (gw_ia_correct_arrays.tph library).                                                         *
 *      - Used Gwendolyne's gw_install_archives function to install new animations (any extracted in /archives folder).                                                                *
 *      - Coding simplification:                                                                                                                                                       *
 *          Replaced READ_SHORT 0x28 and WRITE_SHORT 0x28 with READ_LONG 0x28 and WRITE_LONG 0x28.                                                                                     *
